name: UntitledGameJam-Ducks
description:
A casual endless runner staring Gerald a little duck. Currently there are no achievements to unlock. I plan on adding to the game later on. I also plan on making it downloadable for PC that's why there is an exit button. In web it will crash, since it's the browser.
